                        "content": "A client receiving therapy with carbidopa/levodopa is upset and tells the home health nurse that the urine has turned a darker color since starting this medication. The client wants to discontinue its use. In formulating a response to the client's concerns, the nurse interprets that this change is indicative of which condition?",
