                        "type": "0",
                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "The nurse is preparing to ambulate a client with Parkinson's disease who has recently been started on levodopa/carbidopa. Before performing this activity with the client, the nurse would include which most important assessment in the client's plan of care?",
