                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nAmantadine is an antiparkinson agent that potentiates the action of dopamine in the central nervous system. The expected effect of therapy is a decrease in akinesia and rigidity. Leukopenia, urinary retention, and hypotension are all side and adverse effects of the medication.",
